---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Tokyo GÆMZ Show" description="Tokyo GÆMZ Show" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.video-embed {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.video-embed iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 0;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
			<strong>Tokyo GÆMZ Show</strong>
			<br>
			Tokyo, Japan
			<br>
			2025
            <br>
            <br>
			Talk: Game Poems
            <br>
            <p>
            Coinciding with Tokyo Game Show, I organized an event focused on experimental games and talks. A call for speakers was announced, and 5 speakers shared a variety of topics. A total of 22 partipants joined.
            </p>
            <strong>Talks</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Grisha - Shader work on the game <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3458890/DOOM_SPIRAL/">Doom Spiral</a></li>
                <li>Joana - Building a not so game industry <a href="https://rect.repair/">art game tech scene </a> in Shanghai</li>
                <li>Darwin - <a href="https://plunderludics.github.io/">Plunderludics / Unityhawk </a></li>
                <li>Adlan - <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DObQfZOEuea/?img_index=4">Anti Gen AI watermarks  </a></li>
                <li>Farfama - <a href="https://www.gamepoemsbook.com/">Game Poems </a> </li>
            <p>Slides for my talk can be found <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1TCq9LkalNPpHwsTQfas7ExeRR9zLTBSpYe34jJqBMeE/edit?usp=sharing">here</a></p>
            
            </ul>
            <br>
            

            <img src="/gaemz/tgs2025_14sep.webp"/>
            <caption> Poster art created by <a href="https://www.thenomi.com/">Til Nomi</a></caption>

		</div>
	</body>
</html>